285
00:25:45,779 --> 00:25:46,391
Mari.

286
00:26:02,787 --> 00:26:06,244
Bukankah Mummy pernah beritahu
kau Tidak baik mengendap Potter?

287
00:26:06,486 --> 00:26:07,451
Petrificus Totalus.

288
00:26:19,253 --> 00:26:20,187
Yalah...

289
00:26:21,096 --> 00:26:23,768
Dia akan mati sebelum kau mampu
mengelap darah dari dagu kau.

290
00:26:29,926 --> 00:26:31,198
Itu untuk Ayahku.

291
00:26:31,581 --> 00:26:33,154
Nikmati perjalanan
kau kembali ke London.

292
00:27:16,949 --> 00:27:17,993
Ennervate.

293
00:27:24,635 --> 00:27:25,623
Hello, Harry.

294
00:27:25,660 --> 00:27:27,542
Luna. Bagaimana kau tahu aku di sini?

