930
01:16:01,140 --> 01:16:02,092
Ada kau dapat burung hantu aku?

931
01:16:02,521 --> 01:16:03,810
Ya.

932
01:16:06,196 --> 01:16:08,940
Kalau Dumbledore pergi, mungkin
berita baik bagi kementerian,

933
01:16:08,976 --> 01:16:11,189
