Ok, baguslah.

1068
01:27:14,544 --> 01:27:16,323
Kau rasa dia macam aku juga ke?

1069
01:27:16,474 --> 01:27:17,483
Aku harap begitu.

1070
01:27:17,525 --> 01:27:19,235
